The Automated Question Builder Application is an innovative tool designed to generate questions from a given text input using advanced natural language processing (NLP) techniques. This project aims to support educators, trainers, and learners by providing a streamlined way to create assessments, quizzes, and study materials. By leveraging AI models, particularly those offered by OpenAI, the application can produce high-quality, relevant questions that enhance learning and comprehension.

The Automated Question Builder Application represents a significant advancement in educational technology, combining the power of AI and NLP to streamline the question generation process. By automating this task, the application not only saves time for educators but also enhances the learning experience for students. As education continues to evolve, tools like this will play a crucial role in supporting effective teaching and learning practices.
